welcome_message_body: Welcome to Kirkland, a charming city known for its beautiful waterfront, vibrant art scene, and friendly community. We invite you to explore our city and enjoy all it has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is a small and efficient building that offers a comfortable waiting area for passengers.

terminals.name: Water Terminal
terminals.description: The water terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is where seaplanes dock and passengers can board and disembark from the aircraft.

wifi.note: WiFi is available in the main terminal and on some seaplanes for an additional fee.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial and private flights at Boeing Field/King County International Airport.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is primarily used for cargo and general aviation flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport handles all commercial flights and houses a variety of amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a more exclusive and personalized experience for travelers.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network for internet access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport, primarily used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport primarily serves Alaska Airlines and its partners.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves international flights and some domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport serves all domestic flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
